Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:11.69,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎苹果、谷歌、推特、Palm\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Apple, Google, Twitter, Palm.{\r}
