Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:23.91,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,我在推特的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}My last job there{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.16,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎最后一份岗位 是高级副总工程师\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}was the senior vice president of engineering.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:29.25,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我曾是Pinterest的总经理\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-I was the president of Pinterest. -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:32.71,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎在那之前 我在脸书做了五年的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Before that, um, I was the... the director of monetization{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.26,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎盈利总监\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}at Facebook for five years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:37.97,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎在推特期间 我用了几年时间 ‎运营他们的开发者平台\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}While at Twitter, I spent a number of years running their developer platform,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:40.22,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎然后我做了消费者产品部长\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and then I became head of consumer product.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:44.27,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我曾合作发明 ‎谷歌硬盘、谷歌邮箱聊天\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I was the coinventor of Google Drive, Gmail Chat,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:46.68,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎脸书网页和脸书“赞”按钮\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Facebook Pages, and the Facebook like button.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:50.77,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎对 所以我才花了八个月的时间\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah. This is... This is why I spent, like, eight months{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:52.77,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎和律师反复周旋\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}talking back and forth with lawyers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:55.40,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎真的让我很崩溃\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}This freaks me out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.78,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我在那里任职的时候\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}When I was there,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:02.91,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,一直觉得 ‎总体上 这是积极的力量\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I always felt like, fundamentally, it was a force for good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.37,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我现在不确定 自己是否还这样想了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I don't know if I feel that way anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:10.58,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎出于对道德伦理的担心 ‎我于2017年6月离开谷歌\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I left Google in June 2017,  due to ethical concerns.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:14.13,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎不仅是担心谷歌的道德伦理 ‎而是对整个产业\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}And... And not just at Google but within the industry at large.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:15.38,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我很担心\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm very concerned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:17.67,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎非常担心\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm very concerned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.80,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎如今 人们很容易忽略一个事实\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's easy today to lose sight of the fact{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:27.81,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这些工具 ‎其实为世界创造了一些美好的东西\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}that these tools actually have created some wonderful things in the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:31.94,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎它们让失去联系的家人重聚 ‎找器官捐赠者\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}They've reunited lost family members. They've found organ donors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:35.61,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎它们为整个世界带来了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I mean, there were meaningful, systemic changes happening{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:37.86,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎有意义的、系统的变革\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}around the world because of these platforms{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:40.20,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这是这些平台积极的一面\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}that were positive!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:44.53,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我认为我们对它的消极一面 ‎过度看轻了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I think we were naive about the flip side of that coin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.58,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎对 这些东西 只要你发布 ‎它们自己就会存活\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah, these things, you release them, and they take on a life of their own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:52.00,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎它们被使用的方式 ‎与你当初的预期大相径庭\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}And how they're used is pretty different than how you expected.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:56.50,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我深信 这些负面的后果 ‎不是任何人刻意为之\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Nobody, I deeply believe, ever intended any of these consequences.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:59.55,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎没有任何一个坏人 没有 绝对没有\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}There's no one bad guy. No. Absolutely not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.60,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎那么问题在哪里？\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}So, then, what's the... what's the problem?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:11.35,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎是否有问题？问题在哪里？\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Is there a problem, and what is the problem?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:20.15,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎是 很难给出一个单一的、简明的…\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah, it is hard to give a single, succinct...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.11,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我在试着谈论很多不同的问题\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I'm trying to touch on many different problems.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:23.57,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎问题在哪里？\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What is the problem?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:32.25,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎NETFLIX 原创纪录片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.34,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎虽然面对越来越多的质疑\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Despite facing mounting criticism,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.67,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这些所谓的大型技术公司却越发壮大\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}the so-called Big Tech names are getting bigger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:40.92,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎整个技术产业 ‎正在面临全新维度的审查\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The entire tech industry is under a new level of scrutiny.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:43.80,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎一项新的研究初步揭示了心理健康\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}And a new study sheds light on the link{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.14,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎与社交媒体使用之间的联系\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}between mental health and social media use.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.47,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎来谈谈最新的研究…\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Here to talk about the latest research...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:51.39,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎…的情况 根本没有保险\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}...is going on that gets no coverage at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:54.10,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎数千万美国人无望地\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Tens of millions of Americans are hopelessly addicted{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.31,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎玩电子设备成瘾\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}to their electronic devices.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.16,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎因为技术 现在你真的能\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}It's exacerbated by the fact{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:04:00.69,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,把自己‎隔离在一个泡泡内\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}that you can literally isolate yourself now{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:00.69,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}‎（你的朋友在照片中圈出了你）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.74,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,周围都是‎与你观点相似的人 ‎瘾性就更加恶化了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}in a bubble, thanks to our technology.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.57,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎虚假新闻变得更发达了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Fake news is becoming more advanced{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:06.78,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎威胁着全世界的社会\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and threatening societies around the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:10.33,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我们12年多以前创造推特的时候 ‎根本没有想到这些\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}We weren't expecting any of this when we created Twitter over 12 years ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:12.50,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎官方说 他们没有理由相信\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}White House officials say they have no reason to believe{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.75,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎俄罗斯网络攻击会停止\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}the Russian cyberattacks will stop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:18.13,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎YouTube被迫专注于清理网站\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}YouTube is being forced to concentrate on cleansing the site.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:21.55,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎如果你和十几岁的孩子去聊\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}TikTok, if you talk to any tween out there...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:24.01,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎他们是绝对不可能删除抖音的…\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}...there's no chance they'll delete this thing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:26.34,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎喂 艾拉 可以帮忙摆桌子吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Hey, Isla, can you get the table ready, please?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.51,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎有一个严肃的问题\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}There's a question about whether social media{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.97,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎社交媒体是否让您的孩子抑郁\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}is making your child depressed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.10,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎艾拉 可以帮忙摆桌子吗？\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Isla, can you set the table, please?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.31,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎整容在青少年中已经十分受欢迎\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}These cosmetic procedures are becoming so popular with teens,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:37.90,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎整容医生甚至造出了一种新病征\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}plastic surgeons have coined a new syndrome for it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.82,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎“图片分享畸形征” ‎指的是年轻的患者想做整容手术\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}"Snapchat dysmorphia," with young patients wanting surgery{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:43.74,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎让自己看上去 ‎更接近加了滤镜的自拍中的样子\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}so they can look more like they do in filtered selfies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.91,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我还是不明白 ‎你为什么让她用那东西\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Still don't see why you let her have that thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.53,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我能怎么办？\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What was I supposed to do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.58,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我是说 她们班上的其他孩子全都有\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}I mean, every other kid in her class had one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:51.16,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎她才11岁\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}She's only 11.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.95,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎卡桑 没人强迫你用\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Cass, no one's forcing you to get one.{\r}
