Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:31.10,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎看他们照片的地方”\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and see their photos."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:35.48,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎但他们没有意识到的是 ‎他们在竞争你的关注\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}But what they don't realize is they're competing for your attention.{\r}
