Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:06.09,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎网络上有过各种服务 ‎我们都认为是免费的\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}There are all these services on the Internet that we think of as free,{\r}
