Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:38.06,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎进行无限追踪获利\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}of everywhere everyone goes by large technology companies{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.35,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎大型技术公司的商业模式\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}whose business model is to make sure{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.85,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎是保证广告商能尽最大可能成功\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}that advertisers are as successful as possible.{\r}
