Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:07.59,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我们现在有了 ‎交易大范围人类期货的市场\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}We now have markets that trade in human futures at scale,{\r}
