Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:19.26,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎让网络公司成为了人类历史上\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}that have made the Internet companies the richest companies{\r}
