Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:31.07,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我想让人们知道的是 ‎他们在网上做的一切\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}What I want people to know is that everything they're doing online{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:34.32,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎都被监控着 被追踪着 被评估着\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}is being watched, is being tracked, is being measured.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:39.62,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎你所做出的每一个行为 ‎都被小心翼翼地监控着、记录着\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Every single action you take is carefully monitored and recorded.{\r}
