Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:22.79,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎所有这些我们不经意间 ‎不断流露出的数据\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}And so, all of this data that we're... that we're just pouring out all the time{\r}
