Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.61,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎拥有最优秀模型的公司就赢了\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and whoever has the best model wins.{\r}
