Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:15.46,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎他们就好像拥有一个 ‎我们的巫毒娃娃化身一样\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}it's almost as if they had this avatar voodoo doll-like model of us.{\r}
