Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:19.47,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎点击过的每一个地方\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}all the clicks we've ever made,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.64,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎我们看过的所有视频 ‎点赞过的所有内容\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}all the videos we've watched, all the likes,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:25.35,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎这些数据都会被返回去 ‎用来建造一个越来越精准的模型\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}that all gets brought back into building a more and more accurate model.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:27.48,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎一旦有了这个模型\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}The model, once you have it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.85,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎就能预判这个人做怎样的事\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}you can predict the kinds of things that person does.{\r}
