Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:51.08,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎-完美 有效果 ‎-接着另一个视频\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}-Perfect. That worked. -Following with another video.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:54.04,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎漂亮 在它开始之前 ‎我们插进去一个运动鞋广告\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}Beautiful. Let's squeeze in a sneaker ad before it starts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:59.72,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎很多这种技术公司有三个主要目标\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}At a lot of technology companies, there's three main goals.{\r}
