Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:03.68,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎增加你的使用 让你一直滑动屏幕\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}to drive up your usage, to keep you scrolling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.14,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎有一个增长目标\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}There's the growth goal:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:08.64,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎让你不断回来 尽可能多地邀请朋友\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}to keep you coming back and inviting as many friends{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:10.73,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎让他们再邀请更多的朋友\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}and getting them to invite more friends.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:13.23,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎还有一个广告目标\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}And then there's the advertising goal:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.98,M - RYANLAUN,,0,0,0,,‎确保一切按照预期发展\N{\fntahoma\fs10\1c&H0080FF&}to make sure that, as all that's happening,{\r}
